dct_title_s: A map of the town of Princeton and vicinity, together with a map of the University campus and a brief description of some of the principal University buildings and athletic facilites. Front side.
dct_description_sm: S.n. Alternate title: Princeton University Campus. With historical notes on Princeton University. Verso: "Princeton and vicinity."
